summary: OVER THE COURSE OF THE LAST 8-MONTHS MY 2004 CADILLAC DTS WINDOWS' MOTOR  (FRONT AND REAR, LEFT AND RIGHT) FAILED TO RAISE THE WINDOWS AFTER THEY HAD BEEN LOWERED.  ONE WINDOW AT A TIME.  THIS IS A PROBLEM ON THIS MODEL YEAR (2004).  MANY OTHERS HAVE HAD THE SAME INCIDENT.  I AM LUCKY IN THAT I HAD A WARRANTY IN EFFECT. *TR
